[raw_stderr] +# Sole Market E-Commerce App
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +FastAPI-Backend mit SQLite-Persistenz und Vanilla-JavaScript-Frontend auf Basis modularer Web Components.
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +## Start
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```bash
[raw_stderr] +pip install -r requirements.txt
[raw_stderr] +uvicorn backend.app.main:app --reload
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Die Anwendung ist danach unter `http://127.0.0.1:8000/` erreichbar. Die API-Endpunkte liegen unter `/api`.
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +## Struktur
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```text
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/main.py
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/database.py
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/models.py
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/schemas.py
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/api/
[raw_stderr] +backend/app/seed.py
[raw_stderr] +frontend/index.html
[raw_stderr] +frontend/components/
[raw_stderr] +frontend/styles/
[raw_stderr] +tests/
[raw_stderr] +requirements.txt
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Beim Start erstellt das Backend die SQLite-Tabellen und seedet den Sneaker-Katalog, sofern die Produkte noch nicht vorhanden sind.
